Padre::Plugin::EmacsMode
========================

This Plugin for Padre provides a subset of emacs keybindings
and some of the look and feel where possible.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Padre

